title: Chewman Demo
description:
Game from http://www.trashplay.com. Chewman is arcade pacman-style game, where you control a daemon from World of Trash. Your main goal is to collect all gold coins in the caves and get to Human&#039;s World, avoiding (or destroying) traps and enemies - an Ancient Order, including nuns, knights, angels and other powerful foes, who come to caves to stop you.
Chewing is fun!

This is demo version of Chewman game (non-mature version of Trashman game). Includes 2 first levels, 1 enemy and few other features.
